Title: Reading and Writing Audio Files in LabVIEW

Summary: Learn how to use LabVIEW to retrieve an audio signal from a
WAV-format file, and how to save an audio signal that you have created 
to a WAV-format file.

Keywords: 
audio
WAV file
scaling
stereo
LabVIEW


